de.must.middle
Class Transaction

java.lang.Object
  de.must.middle.Transaction

public class Transaction
extends java.lang.Object

A transaction which may be interrupted to ask user to confirm the process. Helpful to separate business logic from user interface technology. Supports synchronous and asynchronous confirmation. JDialogs may be used for synchronous confirmation, e.g. StandardDialog In other cases repeat transaction check process after calling setConfirmed for the already confirmed aspect of the transaction check.

See Also:
StandardDialog
